[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    343[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      control or vs. standard)                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    344[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Time commitment and visit schedule                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    345[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Risks and potential benefits, balanced              │
