[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    347[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      trials)                                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    348[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Logistics (locations, what is paid for,             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    349[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      compensation framework if any)                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    350[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Candidate's rights (can stop at any time, can       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    351[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      decline to answer questions, etc.)                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    352[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    353[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Adapt to candidate]                                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    354[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Reading level (default 6th-to-8th grade,            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    355[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      configurable per trial and per candidate)           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    356[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Language (institution's supported languages with    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    357[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      validated translations)                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    358[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Pace (candidate-driven, not bot-pushed)             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    359[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Channel (chat, voice, app)                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    360[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    361[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Tone discipline]                                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    362[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Informative, neutral, balanced                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    363[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Not enthusiastic or persuasive                      │
