[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    373[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── STRUCTURED PRE-SCREENING ─────────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    374[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    375[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [IRB-approved pre-screening question set]              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    376[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Subset of protocol's eligibility criteria, written  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    377[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      in plain language with IRB approval                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    378[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Categorical inclusion (does the candidate have the  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    379[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      condition the trial is studying)                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    380[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Categorical exclusion (does the candidate have      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    381[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      characteristics that would exclude them)            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    382[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Where consented and where chart-context is          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    383[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      available, chart-context confirmation supplements   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    384[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      candidate-reported data                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    385[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    386[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Interactive pre-screening]                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    387[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Candidate can ask follow-up questions about why a   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    388[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      question is being asked                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    389[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Candidate can decline to answer specific questions  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    390[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      (with appropriate handling: skip, defer to          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    391[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      coordinator, or treat as "unknown")                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    392[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Candidate can request to talk to a person at any    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    393[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      time (warm handoff)                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    394[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    395[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Pre-screening outcome]                                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    396[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - "appears potentially eligible" (non-binding)        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    397[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - "appears not eligible" (non-binding, with reason)   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    398[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - "needs coordinator review" (ambiguous, partial      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    399[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      data, or judgment call)                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    400[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Pre-screening outcome is non-binding; formal        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    401[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      eligibility is determined by the research           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    402[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      coordinator and (where applicable) the principal    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    403[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      investigator                                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    404[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    405[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    406[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: pre-screening outcome with version-stamped    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    407[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    question set and candidate responses]                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    408[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    409[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
