[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    415[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - System prompt with explicit consent-process-        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    416[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      exclusion, balanced-presentation discipline,        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    417[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      neutral-tone discipline, and citation requirement   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    418[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Tool surface:                                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    419[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      - trial_materials_retrieve (IRB-approved candidate- │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    420[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │        facing materials)                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    421[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      - prescreening_question_retrieve (current question  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    422[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │        set with IRB-approved version)                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    423[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      - trial_logistics_retrieve (visit schedule,         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    424[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │        locations, compensation framework)                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    425[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      - alternative_trials_retrieve (other trials the     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    426[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │        candidate may be eligible for)                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    427[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      - chart_context_retrieve (where consented and       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    428[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │        authenticated)                                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    429[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      - clinician_notification_propose (where consented)  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    430[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      - coordinator_handoff_propose                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    431[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      - follow_up_schedule_propose                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    432[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    433[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Scope discipline]                                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    434[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Within-scope: plain-language trial information,     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    435[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      pre-screening, logistics, candidate rights, basic   │
