[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    438[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      enrollment commitment, medical advice ("should I do │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    439[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      this trial"), insurance-coverage questions beyond   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    440[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      basic framework, legal advice, other-patient        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    441[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      experiences (which the bot does not have access to) │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    442[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    443[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Citation discipline]                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    444[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Every assertion grounded in cited IRB-approved      │
