[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    455[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── OUTPUT SAFETY + BALANCED-PRESENTATION CHECK ──┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    456[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    457[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Standard output safety primitives from recipe 11.1]   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    458[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Scope filter (no consent-process delivery, no       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    459[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      enrollment commitment, no medical advice)           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    460[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Vendor-managed guardrail layer                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    461[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    462[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Trial-recruitment-specific verification]              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    463[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - All assertions grounded in cited IRB-approved       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    464[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      materials                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    465[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Citation includes content_id, content_version,      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    466[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      IRB_approval_reference                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    467[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Balanced-presentation check: response presents      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    468[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      risks alongside benefits, control alongside         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    469[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      experimental, alternatives alongside the trial      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    470[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Persuasion-and-pressure check: response does not    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    471[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      use persuasive techniques, urgency framing, or      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    472[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      "closing" patterns                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    473[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Consent-process-drift check: response does not      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    474[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      deliver consent-process content                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    475[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Disclosure language present where required          │
