[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    479[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    480[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: response cleared, replaced with safer         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    481[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    template, or regenerated with corrections]            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    482[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                          │
