[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    484[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    485[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── INTEREST ASSESSMENT + COORDINATOR HANDOFF ────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    486[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    487[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Interest assessment]                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    488[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Neutral framing: "Would you like me to connect you  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    489[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      with a research coordinator?"                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    490[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Yes / No / Let-me-think-about-it responses recorded │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    491[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - "Let me think about it" supports follow-up with     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    492[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      consent and time-limited cadence                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    493[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    494[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Warm handoff for interested candidates]               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    495[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Synchronous handoff: bot bridges to coordinator     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    496[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      via chat, voice, or video where coordinator is      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    497[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      reachable; conversation context attached            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    498[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Asynchronous handoff: bot tells candidate when to   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    499[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      expect coordinator contact and what next steps look │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    500[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      like; coordinator gets full context and pre-        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    501[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      screening outcome before contact                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    502[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    503[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Handoff payload]                                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    504[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Conversation transcript                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    505[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Pre-screening outcome with non-binding caveat       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    506[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Trial of interest                                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    507[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Candidate's stated preferences (preferred contact   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    508[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      method, contact time)                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    509[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Candidate's stated questions and concerns           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    510[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Bot's structured summary                            │
